{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/web/react/useMemo&useCallback/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"升高"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"6bc712c0-d8a2-58dc-a51a-bed8039cff3f","excerpt":"1 背景 在用 taro 写小程序，偶然间遇到了个问题。用 useCallback 生成了一个 memoized 函数，但是在重复渲染的时候，memoized 函数执行后内部所依赖的变量仍旧是旧的。 原因已经找到，因为没有传递第二个依赖项数组。翻阅了 react 文档和一些 blog。对这两个 hook…","html":"<h2>1 背景</h2>\n<p>在用 taro 写小程序，偶然间遇到了个问题。用 useCallback 生成了一个 memoized 函数，但是在重复渲染的时候，<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Memoization\">memoized</a> 函数执行后内部所依赖的变量仍旧是旧的。</p>\n<p>原因已经找到，因为没有传递第二个依赖项数组。翻阅了 react 文档和一些 blog。对这两个 hook 做个学习记录。</p>\n<h2>2 解释</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> useCallback<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token constant\">T</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>args<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">any</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token builtin\">any</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  callback<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">T</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  deps<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> DependencyList\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">T</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token generic-function\"><span class=\"token function\">useMemo</span><span class=\"token generic class-name\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token constant\">T</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">factory</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token constant\">T</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> deps<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> DependencyList <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">undefined</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">T</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>从 react 官方文档对两个函数的定义可以知道，useCallback 中 T 为一个函数，而在 useMemo 中，<strong>由于传入 <code class=\"language-text\">useMemo</code> 的函数会在渲染期间执行</strong> ，所以 T 为执行结果。</p>\n<p>useCallback(fn, deps) 相当于 useMemo(() => fn, deps)。</p>\n<h2>3 作用</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">对函数进行缓存，以便于</code></pre></div>\n<h2>4 使用场合</h2>","frontmatter":{"title":"useCallback 和 useMemo","date":"July 21, 2022","description":"useCallback 和 useMemo"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/web/javascript/ui-components/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"如何开发一个 UI 组件库"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/web/react/hook/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"hook"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"6bc712c0-d8a2-58dc-a51a-bed8039cff3f","previousPostId":"3e621a3d-3416-54ce-8ff9-71867e01839d","nextPostId":"6dfb1cde-e5eb-5032-a2e0-ccac59e80830"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383"]}